  "name": "no-stock",
  "body": "<div>Hi {{ticket.requester.first_name}},&nbsp;</div><div><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Thank you for your message.&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">We are writing to inform you that due to a stock sync error we cannot fulfil your order.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">We have looked for an alternative product, but we do not have anything available to offer you at this time.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Sadly, our only option is to cancel your order and process a full refund.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">The refund will reflect in your account within the next 3-5 business days.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Thank you for your understanding.&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Kind regards,&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;\">Mac Group Customer Service&nbsp;</span></div>",
